---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Founders">
	<main class="section">
		<div class="container" data-reveal>
			<h2>Founders</h2>
			<p style="margin-top: -0.4rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 900px;">
				Meet the leadership behind Paramount World Records—built by story makers and standard setters.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="container profile-grid" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
			<article class="profile-card card-gloss" data-reveal>
				<img
					src="/images/founders/arun.png"
					alt="Mr. Arun, Founder and CEO"
					style="width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; object-position: 50% 35%; border: 2px solid rgba(120,178,230,0.78); margin-bottom: 0.9rem;"
				/>
				<p class="profile-role">Arun (BigGuy Arun) - Founder & CEO</p>
				<div class="profile-text">
					<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">From Media Veteran to Global Record Authority</h3>
					<p style="margin: 0 0 0.8rem;">
						With over 9 years of high-stakes media experience across two premier television channels, Arun—
						widely known as BigGuy Arun—has dedicated his career to spotlighting excellence. Currently the
						Anchor and Director of <strong>“Varthaga Paarvai”</strong> on Tamilan TV, he leads one of the most
						esteemed interview platforms for India’s top entrepreneurs.
					</p>

					<h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.6rem;">A Proven Record of Human Potential</h3>
					<p style="margin: 0 0 0.8rem;">
						Arun doesn’t just verify records; he breaks them. He is a <strong>3-Time World Record Holder</strong>
						in categories that push the absolute limits of the human mind and body:
					</p>
					<ul class="suggestions" style="margin-top: 0;">
						<li>The Longest Training Marathon: A testament to physical endurance.</li>
						<li>The Longest Social Talk Marathon: A feat of communication and mental stamina.</li>
						<li>The 12-Hour Speed Write: The fastest book ever written and released online in under 12 hours.</li>
					</ul>

					<h3 style="margin: 0.9rem 0 0.6rem;">The Vision for Paramount</h3>
					<p style="margin: 0;">
						After achieving his own global milestones, Arun realized that the world’s most ambitious dreamers
						lacked a platform that truly understood their journey. Driven by a mission to turn
						<strong>“potential into legacy”</strong>, he co-founded Paramount World Records with Mrs. Preeti Gupta.
						Together, they have built a registry designed by achievers, for achievers—ensuring that every
						extraordinary feat gets the global recognition it deserves.
					</p>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article class="profile-card card-gloss" data-reveal>
				<img
					src="/images/founders/preeti.png"
					alt="Mrs. Preeti Gupta, Co-Founder and Director"
					style="width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; object-position: 50% 20%; border: 2px solid rgba(120,178,230,0.78); margin-bottom: 0.9rem;"
				/>
				<p class="profile-role">Preeti Gupta - Co-Founder & Director</p>
				<div class="profile-text">
					<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">The Architect of Stories & Standards</h3>
					<p style="margin: 0 0 0.8rem;">
						As a Director at Paramount World Records, Mrs. Preeti Gupta brings a unique fusion of creative vision
						and strategic precision. With over seven years of experience in storytelling and media, she is a proud
						member of the Screenwriters Association, recognized for expertise as a concept, screenplay and dialogue
						writer. Her creative fire is backed by academic excellence, holding an <strong>MBA in Finance</strong>, which
						ensures Paramount is built on a foundation of transparency and global standards.
					</p>

					<h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.6rem;">A Record-Breaking Visionary</h3>
					<p style="margin: 0 0 0.8rem;">
						Preeti doesn’t just manage the registry; she leads by example. She is a World Record Holder for her
						extraordinary literary speed, having written <strong>15 original short stories in just one hour</strong>.
						This firsthand experience in the record-breaking arena allows her to deeply connect with the ambitious
						individuals Paramount seeks to support.
					</p>

					<h3 style="margin: 0.9rem 0 0.6rem;">The Modern Working Woman</h3>
					<p style="margin: 0 0 0.8rem;">
						Beyond her professional accolades, Preeti embodies the spirit of the modern woman. As the wife of a
						Chartered Accountant and a nurturing mother, she masterfully balances the demands of family life with
						the pursuit of professional excellence.
					</p>

					<h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.6rem;">A Legacy of Inspiration</h3>
					<p style="margin: 0;">
						Co-founding Paramount alongside BigGuy Arun, Preeti’s mission is to create a globally respected
						platform that celebrates talent from all walks of life—so the next generation can move beyond comfort
						zones and create milestones that become history.
					</p>
				</div>
			</article>
		</div>

		<div class="container" data-reveal style="margin-top: 2rem;">
			<div class="panel">
				<h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.6rem;">Founders’ Alignment</h2>
				<p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
					Arun leads the storytelling voice and applicant experience, while Preeti strengthens the standards and verification framework.
					Together, they ensure Paramount remains premium, trustworthy, and future-ready.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

